  "An offshore drilling platform in deep water experiences a blowout, spilling millions of barrels of oil into a productive fishing area. The spill response is hampered by inadequate technology for deep-water containment. Initial cleanup estimates prove wildly low. Based on the Deepwater Horizon experience, which policy lesson is most important?": "",
